\n<\N[5]>\F[62]Um... I have something I want to ask everyone
right away.

\F[62]Skipping the greetings, I quickly took the lead
and started. There was something I
really wanted to confirm first.

\n<\N[5]>\F[62]I heard that the three of you had a
relationship with Director Udo. Is there
any chance that you were being
blackmailed because of that?
\n<Kino>\F[62]\FF[91]\AA[FF]Hmm... huh? Did we not talk about it?

\F[62]\FF[91]\AA[FF]Kino sends a gaze towards Sawa and throws a
question at them.
\n<Sawa>\F[62]\FF[93]\AA[FF]That... um... I'm sorry...
\n<\N[5]>\F[62]\FF[93]\AA[F]......What do you mean?

\n<Momo>\F[62]\FF[92]\AA[FF]Ahh... It's difficult to talk about it with
Sawa-chan. Well... to put it simply...

\n<Momo>\F[62]\FF[92]\AA[FF]All three of us... we were caught on camera
engaging with the director. And, well,
the director has the explicit video
file...
\n<\N[5]>\F[62]\FF[92]\AA[F]Hmm... I see, so that's how it is...

\F[62]The dark rumors about Director Udo... and
the reasons why they follow him. It's
not something to be happy about, but it
seems like my thoughts were on target.

\F[62]Even if it's just a hypothetical situation,
I feel bad for the two of them... but I
can somehow imagine the reasons why Kino
and Momo sided with the director.

\F[62]In Kino's case, if the reason is that they
usually flatter someone in power and
have a future in mind... I can
understand. And in Momo's case, as she
herself said, I can understand that she
ended up choosing the more enjoyable
path.

\F[62]However... I couldn't quite wrap my head around
the fact that Sawa was on the director's
side, so I came to the conclusion that
they must be being blackmailed or have
some kind of weakness.

\n<\N[5]>\F[62]\FF[93]\AA[F](However... in such a situation, is Sawa helping
us?)

\n<\N[5]>\F[62]\FF[93]\AA[F](Is it okay for me to act on my own like
this... If Udo finds out, won't it cause
trouble for Sawa?)

\F[62]\FF[93]\AA[FF]......I gaze at Sawa. After Sawa returns my
gaze with a curious expression, they
lower their head.

\n<Kino>\F[62]\FF[91]\AA[FF]...So, is that all you wanted to talk about? I
was woken up from my sleep, so I want to
go back to sleep...

\n<\N[5]>\F[62]\FF[91]\AA[F]...I'm sorry, there's one more thing I want to
ask the two of you. This is the main
topic.

\F[62]\FF[91]\AA[F]I gathered my resolve, fueled by the
uncertainty that arose, and continued
with my questioning.

\n<\N[5]>\F[62]\FF[91]\AA[F]Did the two of you know that there was a
master key for the mansion? Or have you
seen any keys that look like it
somewhere?
\n<Momo>\F[62]\FF[92]\AA[FF]Hmm... Momo doesn't know and hasn't seen it.

\n<Kino>\F[62]\FF[91]\AA[FF]I haven't seen a key like that either...
ahh...!
\n<\N[5]>\F[62]\FF[91]\AA[F]Kino? Do you remember anything?

\F[62]\FF[91]\AA[F]Kino placed a hand on their mouth and was
lost in thought.

\n<Kino>\F[62]\FF[91]\AA[FF]Huh? Ah... When you say 'key', that thing...
was it a key? No, when I first came to
this mansion, I saw something like that
in the guardhouse...
\n<\N[5]>\F[62]\FF[91]\AA[F]Where is it?! Do you have it, Kino?!

\n<Kino>\F[62]\FF[91]\AA[FF]Well... if you're asking if I have it, then no,
I don't have it~...
\n<Momo>\F[62]\FF[92]\AA[FF]Ahaha, Kino-chan, your eyes are swimming~♪

\n<Sawa>\F[62]\FF[93]\AA[FF]That's the face you make when your stupid
pranks get exposed, Kino... Come on,
just spill it already.

\n<Kino>\F[62]\FF[91]\AA[FF]...No, it was pure gold... I thought it might
be valuable... So, the angel and devil
inside me waged a fierce battle...

\n<\N[5]>\F[62]\FF[91]\AA[F]In the end, the devil emerged victorious.
What did you do with the key? I hope you
didn't already sell it or something...

\n<Kino>\F[62]\FF[91]\AA[FF]Sell it?! What do you take me for?! At that
time, I was suddenly called by the
director and threw it into a locker with
a \C[2] key... What happened again?

\F[62]\FF[91]\AA[FF]Kino looked up and struck their fist into
their palm, assuming a classic pose,
then opened their mouth again.

\n<Kino>\F[62]\FF[91]\AA[FF]Oh, right! I closed the locker and kicked
the key underneath it! Oh man, I was so
panicked at that time.
\n<\N[5]>\F[62]\FF[93]\AA[F]Sawa, can you get it?

\n<Sawa>\F[62]\FF[93]\AA[FF]Yes! I'll go right awa-- Ah! I'm sorry... It

\n<Sawa>\F[62]\FF[93]\AA[FF]I think it's about time for the private

lesson room...

are on the director's side.)
